<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idebf8b8b6-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53" identifier="/us/usc/t51/s50701"><num value="50701">§ 50701.</num><heading> Definition of Office</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter, the term “Office” means the Office of Space Commerce established in <ref href="/us/usc/t51/s50702">section 50702 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idebf8b8b7-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/314/s3">Pub. L. 111–314, § 3</ref>, <date date="2010-12-18">Dec. 18, 2010</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/3408">124 Stat. 3408</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/114/90/tIII/s301/b">Pub. L. 114–90, title III, § 301(b)</ref>, <date date="2015-11-25">Nov. 25, 2015</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/129/720">129 Stat. 720</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
